abstract: It was starting to look like business as usual at the Korean Grand Prix as the Red Bull cars of Mark Webber and Sebastian Vettel finished first and second in qualifying. It also looked like almost no business at the circuit on the southern tip of South Korea as few spectators attended the preliminary sessions.

headline.main: Red Bull Strong Again; Attendance Lags in Korea
